        "subject": "LU-7734 lnet: LNET_PINGINFO_SIZE vs LNET_RTR_PINGINFO_SIZE",
        "message": "LU-7734 lnet: LNET_PINGINFO_SIZE vs LNET_RTR_PINGINFO_SIZE\n\nChange LNET_PINGINFO_SIZE so that it takes the number of NIDS\nas a parameter, to prepare for resizing lnet_ping_info_t data.\n\nFor the router pinger add LNET_RTR_PINGINFO_SIZE, fixed at\nLNET_MAX_RTR_NIS (16) interfaces.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Olaf Weber <olaf@sgi.com>\nChange-Id: Ia8468f88059954e91a08b4348bf960cd7e14b3a8\n"
